data.description: Welcome home!!! This 2 Bedroom/1 Bathroom ranch sits on 0.6740 secluded acres in the heart of Suffield Township. This home features an open floor plan concept where the Eat-In Kitchen that has an island is open to the Living Room area. A glass sliding door off the Kitchen gives access to the scenic backyard and patio area. There is a hallway off the Kitchen that leads to a storage closet, bathroom, and the two bedrooms. There is a full unfinished basement with endless opportunities offering plenty of storage space and the potential of being finished to add additional living space. Outside of the house you will find a one car detached garage with a storage room off the back. The back yard is spectacular with views of the neighbor’s pond. This home is conveniently located close to Hartville, Brimfield, Mogadore, & Kent. This home in addition to its furnace has an Outdoor Wood Burner, the Outdoor Wood Burner may or may not convey depending on the purchase price. The great news is a new roof, siding, and gutters will be put on the house and a new roof on the garage. The work has not been started yet and the Sellers are willing to work with any Buyers with letting them choose the colors out if the materials have not already been ordered to do the work. Don’t hesitate and schedule a showing today, you do not want to miss out on this wonderful opportunity.
